From 703e7ac529712e55208c78ac1235dcb319ceeb30 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Fri, 10 Jul 2026 05:50:07 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add ecommerce: shared cart, checkout, and Stripe payments
 across / and /v2
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Extract products into src/lib/catalog.ts (typed, server-safe, single
  source of truth for prices; /v2 adds the Press Club item)
- Shared CartContext with localStorage persistence; one CartDrawer
  mounted in the root layout so both concepts use the same cart
- Wire the dead 'Add to cart' buttons in Products (v1) and V2Rail,
  and the 'Cart · 0' buttons in both navs to live counts
- /checkout page (Verdale design language) with order summary
- /api/checkout creating Stripe Checkout Sessions with server-side
  price lookup and qty limits (client can never set prices)
- Demo mode when STRIPE_SECRET_KEY is unset; /checkout/success links
  back to both concepts; .env.example documents setup
- Note: Press Club is charged as a one-time first-quarter payment;
  true recurring billing needs a Stripe recurring price + webhooks
